high_descs: Turn and move to stand in front of the kitchen sink.
Open the cupboard on the left above the sink and remove the dish sponge.
Turn around and carry the sponge to the stove.
Place the sponge in the pan on the right.
Pick up the pan with the sponge inside from the stove.
Turn right and carry the pan with the sponge inside to the sink.
Place the pan and sponge in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a sponge inside a pan in the sink.

high_descs: Turn to the right and walk to face the cabinet above the sink.
Pick up the sponge in the left side cabinet above the sink.
Turn around and walk across the room, then turn right to face the stove.
Place the sponge in the pot on the front right burner.
Pick up the pot with the sponge in it on the front right burner.
Turn right and walk across the room to face the sink.
Place the pot with a sponge in it into the sink.
anns.task_desc: To put a sponge in a pot as well as place them in the sink.

high_descs: turn right towards the shelf
pick up the sponge
turn around towards the gas
drop the sponge on the pan on the gas
pick up the pan
turn right and move to the sink
drop the pan on the sink
anns.task_desc: drop a pan with a spoon in it on the sink
